title: Virtual Clone Drive 5 (Virtual Drive)
description:
a good alternative to Daemon Tools

Virtual Clone Drive lets you make virtual drives from disk images such as ISO and other popular formats.

Instead of burning a disc image to a CD or DVD you can mount it to a virtual drive with this software which saves you from wasting CDs and DVDs also for things such as games they run a lot faster using a virtual drive instead of a CD or DVD
